oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Photograph of a camp scene
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: This photograph shows a large encampment surrounded by hills. The encampment includes tents but also what appear to be buildings in the center of the camp. A road runs into the camp as do phone or electrical lines. A car is visible on the road. The location of the camp is unknown.
